; Regression test for issue #2095
; The 'D' directive sets a default commodity that is applied to subsequent
; commodityless amounts (plain numbers) seen while parsing the journal.
; This mirrors hledger's 'D' directive behaviour.

D 1000.00 $

2022-01-01 Groceries
  Expenses:Food     10
  Assets:Cash      -10

test reg Expenses:Food
22-Jan-01 Groceries             Expenses:Food               10.00 $      10.00 $
end test

test bal Expenses:Food
             10.00 $  Expenses:Food
end test
